Hidden Camera 5: Shipped Out In The Morning
October 11, 2013
Barbara is grilling some dogs on the grill for her husband who will be coming home a little later. Suddenly someone arrives at the gate and startles her. It's her boyfriend from five years ago and he's a marine now. He came to say goodbye before being shipped off to war. Sound familiar? Yeah, it's a classic! Barbara knows she doesn't want anything to do with this guy, but how can she resist his situation? What she doesn't know is that her devoted husband recently installed external security cameras around the house. He didn't happen to mention the fact yet. Why would he? They're outside - it's not like he's trying to spy on her.
